declarations.name: fixtureURL
declarations.description: Returns a formatted URL for a given Storybook fixture.

declarations.name: renderComponent
declarations.description: A helper that returns a function to bind a Storybook story to a ViewTemplate.

declarations.name: renderViewTemplate
declarations.description:
Renders a ViewTemplate as elements in a DocumentFragment.
Bindings, such as event binding, will be active.

declarations.name: createStory
declarations.description:
Renders a FAST `html` template as a story.
